Job Details
SERVICE TECHNICIANS
Required for Crawford Door M.E. Candidates should send along with their Curriculum Vitae the following documents:
Prerequisites: - Driving licence of GCC - Preferable but not a must - Electrical Certificate - ITI or diploma (attested from the UAE embassy outside UAE, from the Ministry of Foreign Affairs)- Copy of passport- Experience - Minimum 3 years- Should possess good communication skills in English
Others: Mechanical Engineering qualification; with experience is also preferable
Interested candidates may send their CV to: The Service ManagerCrawford Door M.E.P.O. Box 80893, Dubai, United Arab EmiratesFax: 009714-8854919Or email to: crawford@emirates.net.ae
